  <h3 id="using-hint-text" class="nhsuk-u-margin-top-8">Using hint text</h3>
  <p>Follow our advice on <a href='/service-manual/components/hint-text'>hint text</a> and this example of hint text with text input.</p>

  {{ designExample({
